\" mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"=\"\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">本身大家用刀切开茄子的时候应该可以发现，茄子内部是比较干燥的，并且用手捏上去感觉有点类似</font><b><spanyes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(101,113,128); letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:bold;text-transform:none;=\"\" font-style:normal;font-size:8.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;=\"\" background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"=\"\">“海绵”</spanyes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(101,113,128);></b><spanyes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(101,113,128); letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;=\"\" font-size:8.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);=\"\" mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"=\"\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">，没有错，正是因为茄子内部具备这样的密集小气孔类似海绵的结构，所以在进行煸炒茄子时，加入的油分就会都被茄子提前吸收，导致前面大家都会下意识的认为自己加入的油加少了，然后就会继续加入一些油，从而导致最后做出来的炒茄子特别油腻，吃一口就吃不下去。</font><spanyes\';font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:\'times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></spanyes\';font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;></spanyes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(101,113,128);></spanyes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(101,113,128);></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><spanyes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(101,113,128); letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;=\"\" font-size:8.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);=\"\" mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"=\"\"><spanyes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(101,113,128); letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;=\"\" font-size:8.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);=\"\" mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"=\"\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><br></font></spanyes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(101,113,128);></spanyes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(101,113,128);></p>', '126', null, null, null, '15', '5', '2019-06-03 22:38:13', '1');
